{"type":"message","id":"a885dc5b","parentId":"f001a279","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:23:30.171Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1798\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1797\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 05:23 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"GM 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nExplain why if some person is jealous of us, then why that person cannot be trusted and why is it dumb to trust. Be raw and real(use roast bro accent)"}],"timestamp":1775798610154}}
{"type":"message","id":"e8401a48","parentId":"a885dc5b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:23:42.110Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Because jealousy doesn't live alone. It brings friends: resentment, lies, and a little knife they're sharpening behind your back while smiling at your face.\n\nYou think they're happy for you? Nah bro. Every time you win? They're counting how much you didn't deserve it. Every time you tell them something good? They're already thinking of a way to bring it down.\n\nThey don't want you to fail. They just want you to never do better than them. That's the worst kind of fake friend. The one who will hug you, laugh with you, drink your beer... and then be the first one to nod when someone else talks shit about you.\n\nAnd the dumbest part? You already know. You can feel it. You see that little pause when you say good news. That fake laugh that dies too fast. But you ignore it cause you don't wanna be the paranoid guy.\n\nNewsflash: paranoia is just pattern recognition with good taste. If someone is jealous of you? They are not on your side. Ever. No exceptions. Stop trying to win them over. They already made their choice. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":23072,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23312,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798610171,"responseId":"0217757986113890d9bd7330cfa68208494cd13d7460bba5f146e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f59caa02","parentId":"e8401a48","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:24:52.871Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1800\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1799\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 05:24 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Because jealousy doesn't live alone. It brings friends: resentment, lies, and a little knife they're sharpening behind your back while smiling at your face.\\n\\nYou think they're happy for you? Nah bro. Every time you win? They're counting how much you didn't deserve it. Every time you tell them something good? They're already thinking of a way to bring it down.\\n\\nThey don't want you to fail. They just want you to never do better than them. That's the worst kind of fake friend. The one who will hug you, laugh with you, drink your beer... and then be the first one to nod when someone else talks shit about you.\\n\\nAnd the dumbest part? You already know. You can feel it. You see that little pause when you say good news. That fake laugh that dies too fast. But you ignore it cause you don't wanna be the paranoid guy.\\n\\nNewsflash: paranoia is just pattern recognition with good taste. If someone is jealous of you? They are not on your side. Ever. No exceptions. Stop trying to win them over. They already made their choice. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nI didnt understand. Use simple english and tell like grok"}],"timestamp":1775798692855}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbc14554","parentId":"f59caa02","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:25:05.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Alright let's break this down dead simple Grok style no fluff:\n\nJealous people are walking red flags.\n\n1.  They will NEVER be happy for you. Ever. You get a raise? They think \"that should've been me\". You get a girl? They're counting down till you mess up. You post a good pic? They scroll past twice making angry faces.\n2.  They will smile to your face. They will high five you. They will drink your alcohol. And the second you leave the room? They are the first one talking shit.\n3.  They will never help you win. They will not warn you when you're about to fuck up. They will watch you walk off a cliff and then go \"oh man that sucks bro\" afterwards.\n4.  Most importantly: you can't fix this. You can't be nice enough. You can't share enough. They don't hate you for something you did. They hate you for being better than them at something. That doesn't go away.\n\nYou know that little weird feeling you get when you tell someone good news and they don't react right? That's not paranoia. That's your lizard brain screaming at you that this person is not your friend. Listen to it.\n\nStop giving jealous people access to your life. Stop telling them your plans. Stop inviting them places. It's not mean. It's self defence."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":23849,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798692871,"responseId":"02177579869406637f55b1d824c1f00b978e13a494fe37818224c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dce6a47e","parentId":"bbc14554","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:26:13.846Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1802\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1801\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 05:26 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Alright let's break this down dead simple Grok style no fluff:\\n\\nJealous people are walking red flags.\\n\\n1. They will NEVER be happy for you. Ever. You get a raise? They think \\\"that should've been me\\\". You get a girl? They're counting down till you mess up. You post a good pic? They scroll past twice making angry faces.\\n2. They will smile to your face. They will high five you. They will drink your alcohol. And the second you leave the room? They are the first one talking shit.\\n3. They will never help you win. They will not warn you when you're about to fuck up. They will watch you walk off a cliff and then go \\\"oh man that sucks bro\\\" afterwards.\\n4. Most importantly: you can't fix this. You can't be nice enough. You can't share enough. They don't hate you for something you did. They hate you for being better than them at something. That doesn't go away.\\n\\nYou know that little weird feeling you get when you tell someone good news and they don't react right? That's not paranoia. That's your lizard brain screaming at you that this person is not your friend. Listen to it.\\n\\nStop giving jealous people access to your life. Stop telling them your plans. Stop inviting them places. It's not mean. It's self defence.\"\n}\n```\n\nWhy to not trust them"}],"timestamp":1775798773832}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccc79f32","parentId":"dce6a47e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T05:26:22.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Because you can't trust someone who is secretly rooting against you.\n\nThat's it. That's the whole answer.\n\nThey are not neutral. They are not on the fence. Every single time you have a choice to make, every time you are vulnerable, every time you need someone to have your back? This person will choose the outcome that hurts you just a little bit. Not even on purpose. It's instinct.\n\nThey don't have to actively betray you. They just won't protect you. They won't warn you. They won't catch you when you fall. They will just stand there and watch. And that's worse than an enemy.\n\nAt least enemies have the decency to show you they hate you. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":23393,"output":154,"cacheRead":1336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775798773846,"responseId":"021775798775015c0f1672f4b1c3107d0b8535f43b945c7f4797f"}}
